{
  "id": "adv_event_2504_02_07",
  "title": "襲撃！大怪獣遙子",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さくら達が時空の狭間から脱出した直後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Right after Sakura and the others escaped the space-time rift",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.9666666269,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_wind-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2033.3333413
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_07/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_07-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……はっ！　こ、ここは……どこ！？\nそれに私……大きくなってる！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm… Hah! W-where… am I!?\nAnd me… I’ve gotten bigger!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9666666746,
      "endTime": 14.2862360716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_wind-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 13.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_07/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_07-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "私、さくらちゃん達と時空の狭間から\n星見プロへ戻っているはずじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was supposed to be returning with Sakura and the others\nfrom the space-time rift to Hoshimi Pro…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4862359762,
      "endTime": 21.486235785399998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_07/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_07-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだわ、さっきさくらちゃんが私の体重に\n耐えきれずに手を放してしまって、逆方向に来たんだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right—earlier Sakura couldn’t handle\nmy weight and let go of my hand‚ so I got sent the other way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6995692332,
      "endTime": 31.732539471,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4666.666666600001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_wind-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 25.156100854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_07/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_07-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　小さい人達が何か訴えかけてるけど……\n小さ過ぎて何を言っているか分からないわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? Those tiny people seem to be trying to tell me something…\nThey’re so small I can’t tell what they’re saying…",
        "id": ""
      },
