      "text": "い、いたっ！　足の裏に何か刺さったわ……\nこれ、バンプロのビルかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-ow! Something stuck into the sole of my foot…\nIs this… Van Pro’s building‚ maybe…?",
        "id": ""
      },
